stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending
    Pending --> Running: Start Workflow
    Running --> Paused: Pause Workflow
    Paused --> Running: Resume Workflow
    Running --> Completed: All Steps Successful
    Running --> Failed: Step Failure
    Running --> Cancelled: User Cancellation
    Failed --> Retrying: Retry Attempt
    Retrying --> Running: Retry Success
    Retrying --> Failed: Retry Exhausted
    Completed --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
